   \n                l1->next = l2;\n                l1 = temp;\n            } else {\n                ListNode* temp = l2->next;\n                l2->next = l1;\n                l2 = temp;\n            }\n            count++;\n        }\n        if(l1){\n            l2->next = l1;\n        }\n    }\n\n    void print(ListNode* head){\n        while(head){\n            cout << head->val << " ";\n            head = head->next;\n        }\n        cout << endl;\n    }\n};\n\nint main(){\n\n    Solution s;\n    ListNode* head = new ListNode(1);\n    //head->next = new ListNode(2);\n    //head->next->next = new ListNode(3);\n    //head->next->next->next = new ListNode(4);\n\n    s.reorderList(head);\n    return 0;\n}\n'

   \n                l1->next = l2;\n                l1 = temp;\n            } else {\n                ListNode* temp = l2->next;\n                l2->next = l1;\n                l2 = temp;\n            }\n            count++;\n        }\n        if(l1){\n            l2->next = l1;\n        }\n    }\n\n    void print(ListNode* head){\n        while(head){\n            cout << head->val << " ";\n            head = head->next;\n        }\n        cout << endl;\n    }\n};\n\nint main(){\n\n    Solution s;\n    ListNode* head = new ListNode(1);\n    //head->next = new ListNode(2);\n    //head->next->next = new ListNode(3);\n    //head->next->next->next = new ListNode(4);\n\n    s.reorderList(head);
